Blockchain Counter Cake.

This recipe simulates a blockchain counter, tracking blocks like layers of
a delicious cake. Each block adds another layer of cryptographic sweetness.

Ingredients.
0 g genesis block
1 g block increment
10 g target blocks

Method.
Take genesis block from refrigerator.
Put genesis block into mixing bowl.
Add block increment.
Fold target blocks into mixing bowl.
Liquefy contents of the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
